node.text: Been working long and hard with family and friends in my community to learn, love, and protect ourselves and gorgeous woodlands with defensible space !!! 🙏🙏🙏❤️❤️❤️

node.text: Some people start their morning with a coffee.  But in Kingstown…. One of those days 🤷‍♂️
